casebody.data:
Cynthia LEE, petitioner,
v.
FAIRFAX COUNTY SCHOOL BOARD, et al. No. 15-1146. Supreme Court of the United States May 16, 2016.

Motion of Camden County East Branch of the N.A.A.C.P., et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.
